Program: Free Thinking
Title: Eimear McBride and Nathan Filer, Mr Burns
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b045xvw4
Last Broadcast Date: Thu 12 Jun 2014
Prize-winning first novelists Eimear McBride and Nathan Filer join Anne McElvoy to discuss literary experimentation. Plus a first night review of the European premiere of Anne Washburn's play Mr Burns which is set in a world without electricity Producer: Ella-Mai Robey.